snippet.title: The Egg Collection - Menu footage
snippet.description:
Please subscribe to our channel!

Check out this little sneak peek of the main menu for the One Night at Flumpty's "The Egg Collection" heading to consoles. This version will contain all the One Night at Flumpty titles! Even has new music composed by ONAF creator Jonochrome. 

#ONAF #FNAF
